---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout 
  title="About Us — FinanceFlow Hub"
  description="Learn about the mission of FinanceFlow Hub, engineered to democratize advanced financial modeling tools for retail investors and business operators."
>
  <div class="min-h-screen flex flex-col justify-between">
    
    <!-- Top Navigation Header -->
    <header class="border-b border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/80 backdrop-blur-md sticky top-0 z-50">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between h-16 sm:h-20">
          
          <!-- Logo & Branding -->
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
            <a href="/" class="flex items-center space-x-3 hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-tr from-brand-600 to-accent-emerald flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-brand-500/20">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h1 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white font-sans">
                  FinanceFlow<span class="text-brand-400">Hub</span>
                </h1>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 hidden sm:block">Advanced Strategic Finance Suite</p>
              </div>
            </a>
          </div>

          <!-- Navigation Links / CTA -->
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
            <a href="/" class="text-slate-400 hover:text-white px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-slate-800 transition-all focus-ring text-xs font-semibold flex items-center space-x-1.5">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18" />
              </svg>
              <span>Back to Calculators</span>
            </a>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Main Content Container -->
    <main class="flex-grow max-w-3xl w-full mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-12 sm:py-16">
      
      <!-- Back Link for Mobile/SEO -->
      <div class="mb-8">
        <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-brand-400 hover:text-brand-300 transition-colors">
          &larr; Back to Calculators
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Article Base -->
      <article class="space-y-8">
        <header class="border-b border-slate-800 pb-6">
          <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight font-sans">About Us</h1>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mt-2 leading-relaxed">Democratizing Advanced Financial Math for Everyday Wealth Builders.</p>
        </header>

        <!-- Section 1 -->
        <section class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-white tracking-wide">Our Mission</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
            At FinanceFlow Hub, we believe that advanced financial math and tax structuring should not be locked behind the expensive retainer walls of institutional wealth managers, CPA firms, or private banking channels. 
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
            Our suite was engineered to democratize institutional-grade financial strategy. We provide independent contractors, retail operators, self-employed professionals, and individual investors with the same quantitative models used by elite financial officers—completely free, open-access, and run entirely local on your device.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 2 -->
        <section class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-white tracking-wide">The Three Core Pillars of the Suite</h2>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 mt-6">
            
            <div class="glass-panel p-5 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 space-y-2">
              <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-brand-300 uppercase tracking-wider">1. Buy, Borrow, Die Portfolio Leverage</h3>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
                We model the exact margin requirements, interest rates, and capital gains tax drag of Securities-Backed Lines of Credit (SBLOC). This helps high-growth retail investors understand the mathematical risks, margin-call drop thresholds, and net cost-of-capital savings before adding leverage to their asset base.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="glass-panel p-5 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 space-y-2">
              <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-accent-emerald uppercase tracking-wider">2. Multi-Jurisdictional Tax Predictor</h3>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
                Choosing a corporate entity is a complex equation of self-employment taxes, salary structures, dividends, and administrative compliance. Our engine models sole proprietorships vs. corporations (LLC/S-Corp in the US, Ltd in the UK, CCPC in Canada, Pty Ltd in Australia) to tell side-hustlers their exact mathematical break-even threshold.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="glass-panel p-5 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 space-y-2">
              <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-accent-rose uppercase tracking-wider">3. Algorithmic Debt pay-off planning</h3>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
                Whether you prefer the psychological progress of the Debt Snowball or the pure mathematical optimization of the Debt Avalanche, our simulator calculates month-by-month repayment schedules, total interest saved, and months saved to help families reclaim financial freedom.
              </p>
            </div>

          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 3 -->
        <section class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-white tracking-wide">Open Source & Client-Side Privacy</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
            Privacy is a critical requirement in finance. We don't want your data, and we don't store your sensitive financial records. All math calculations, liability amounts, tax figures, and portfolio balances are processed on your local device's JavaScript runtime, retaining 100% of your data privately in your browser.
          </p>
        </section>
      </article>

    </main>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="border-t border-slate-800 bg-slate-950/90 py-10 text-xs text-slate-400">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 space-y-6">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between gap-6">
          <!-- Copyright & Disclaimer info -->
          <div class="max-w-xl space-y-2">
            <p class="font-semibold text-slate-300">
              &copy; 2026 FinanceFlow Hub. All rights reserved.
            </p>
            <p class="text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
              Disclaimer: The calculators provided on this website are for informational and educational purposes only and do not constitute professional financial or legal advice.
            </p>
          </div>
          <!-- Legal & Info links -->
          <nav class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-6 gap-y-2 text-slate-400" aria-label="Footer Navigation">
            <a href="/about" class="hover:text-white transition-colors font-medium">About Us</a>
            <a href="/contact" class="hover:text-white transition-colors font-medium">Contact Us</a>
            <a href="/privacy-policy" class="hover:text-white transition-colors font-medium">Privacy Policy</a>
            <a href="/terms-conditions" class="hover:text-white transition-colors font-medium">Terms & Conditions</a>
          </nav>
        </div>
        <div class="border-t border-slate-900 pt-4 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-2 text-slate-600">
          <p>Calculations are estimates. All financial strategies contain risk.</p>
          <p>Hosted on Cloudflare Pages.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </footer>

  </div>
</Layout>
